Cross-dresser Bobrisky has claimed he’s finer than most girls in Nigeria. He spoke after a lady shared a photo of an Instagram celebrity which went viral. According to the unidentified lady, she bumped into Bobrisky at Ikeja and was left totally shocked at the state of his skin, which she described as ‘terrible.’ Sharing the photo, the lady wrote: “Please don’t let the Instagram picture deceive you. This is a disg*sting picture of Bobrisky that I took yesterday. Omo, skin was irritating.   Benefits of having celebrity parents, by Priscilla Ojo     Prayer, fasting with my pastor got me on Nigerian idol show…     K1 advises upcoming musicians to shun drugs   “For those of you planning to look fresh like Instagram Bobrisky be informed.” Amid being called out and blasted for his look, Bobrisky in a recent post via his Instagram page protested. He said: “I look better than 80% girls in Nigeria… yes, I repeat. I get swag, money, connection pass these girls.” The 30-year-old cross-dresser further warned critics to ensure their account balance is fat before coming to his page to shade him. He added: Please if you wanna argue with me, check your account balance before you open that dirty mouth.”